# Chart images are derived/visual artifacts, not canonical research data.
# The ledger's reproducibility guarantee is over trades_*.csv (hashed),
# not over PNGs — matplotlib embeds its own version string in PNG
# metadata, so byte-identical output across environments/versions isn't
# achievable (or meaningful) for these files. Regenerate via main.py.
research/equity_*.png
research/charts/
